    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deliver packages in a world where everything’s out to kill you, escape wild hazards and enemies, fight back using wacky power-ups and choose from a variety of perks to improve your chances of survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DELIVER PACKAGES ON TIME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against time to deliver packages, navigate the chaos and outsmart enemies. Every delivery is a high-stakes mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/66a63504e003d2effeccd391155c40f6.poster.avif?t=1759335881\" width=480 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/66a63504e003d2effeccd391155c40f6.webm?t=1759335881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/66a63504e003d2effeccd391155c40f6.mp4?t=1759335881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ESCAPE CRAZY OBSTACLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump and dash to weave your way through a barrage of outrageous obstacles. Jump on cars for an extra boost, climb on buildings to escape the mayhem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/e9d02ddeeef1a94d8dea27af6d903753.poster.avif?t=1759335881\" width=480 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/e9d02ddeeef1a94d8dea27af6d903753.webm?t=1759335881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/e9d02ddeeef1a94d8dea27af6d903753.mp4?t=1759335881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT BACK WITH WACKY POWER-UPS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect wild power-ups, blast enemies, boost your speed and defy gravity with outrageous abilities. Take control of the chaos and survive against all odds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/04b1dd81d1a1c3a2cec1df10648cb525.poster.avif?t=1759335881\" width=480 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/04b1dd81d1a1c3a2cec1df10648cb525.webm?t=1759335881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/04b1dd81d1a1c3a2cec1df10648cb525.mp4?t=1759335881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR PLAY STYLE WITH PERKS </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between deliveries, choose from over 50+ unique perks that dramatically change how you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/1f9f00d120e954307e5d6fef9115f8cc.poster.avif?t=1759335881\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/1f9f00d120e954307e5d6fef9115f8cc.webm?t=1759335881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241560/extras/1f9f00d120e954307e5d6fef9115f8cc.mp4?t=1759335881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50+ perks to alter your play style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple unique characters with special abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ power-ups </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different biomes with unique set of challenges, hazards and enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
